{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6b2bf710f","title":"视察山东时的谈话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"781aeb35d7","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":9,"articleId":"f6b2bf710f"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7fe419652e","type":"title","text":"视察山东时的谈话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"75b7fc4888","type":"paragraph","text":"计划、指示不经过群众辩论，主意是你们的；辩论后，群众自已是主人了，干劲自然更足。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"2a8b99541f","type":"paragraph","text":"领导必须多到下面去看，帮助基层干部总结经验，就地进行领导。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"ffab02f5da","type":"paragraph","text":"还是办人民公社好，它的好处是，可以把工、农、商、学、兵合在一起，便于领导。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"9df235abc4","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的小米长得不好嘛，我看群众的干劲太少！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"020fbc4576","type":"paragraph","text":"好，你这个人（历城县北园乡北园农业社主任李书成）不干就不干，一干就大干的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"197b867f1d","type":"paragraph","text":"你好，你（山东省农科所副所长秦杰）学的学问能用上了。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"dca17a9948","type":"paragraph","text":"是应该压追你们一下，不压追，你们就不会上梁山。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"62c1dc01dd","type":"paragraph","text":"你们研究一下棉花为什么落桃，棉花落桃的问题，是否可以研究个办法，叫它少落或不落。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"47c961e756","type":"paragraph","text":"你们行还是农民行","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"45e8d3dfb1","type":"paragraph","text":"那很好，你们要继续努力，力争上游。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"},{"id":"aa1391e388","type":"paragraph","text":"你们十得很好，都鼓足了干劲","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f"}],"page":{"id":"888b4f096f","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","start":520,"end":520}}}},"__N_SSG":true}